MojoPub - A simple Mojolicious & MongoDB based CMS.

MojoPub is a CMS that gets out of your way and makes publishing content easy.

Features:

* Visual content editor (currently Raptor Editor) with upload option
* Easily themeable with bootstrap-based admin & default theme
* Advanced SEO options by default

Roadmap:

* Easy to use (for people who don't know Perl)
* Easy to install (for people who don't know Perl)
* SEO friendly right out of the box (unlike Wordpress)
* Not bug ugly (unlike a lot of Perl-based CMSs out there!)